<title>mdywn ạlqlb yḥmdk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mdywn ạlqlb yḥmdk .. mdywn ạlfm ymjdk)2
 [(ʿlsẖạn ạ̹nt ạlly bmwtk)2 .. njytny mn ạlkẖṭyẗ]2
 ạlqrạr- (mdywn)3 ạ̉nạ mdywn .. mdywn lk yạ ḥbyby
 [(mdywn)3 ạ̉nạ mdywn .. msẖ qạdr ạ̉wfy dywny]2
 2- ạ̉nạ ạlly bqsạwty .. ṣlbtk rby bạ̹ydyã
 [(wạ̹nt ạlly ḥbytny)2 .. wạʿtṭny ḥyạẗ ạ̉bdyẗ]2
 3- (mdywn lk bkl ḥyạty .. ạlly whbthạ lyã)2
 [(mdywn lk btḥryry)2 .. mn kl ạlʿbwdyẗ]2
 4- (ạ̹nt ạlly ʿynk ʿlyã .. wqlbk byḥn ʿlyã)2
 [(ạ̹sẖbʿny byk wạrwyny)2 .. wạḥmyny mn ạlkẖṭyẗ]2</lyrics>
</song>